title: NFL Week 7 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 7 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- recap Week 7 in the NFL including the Rams upset over the Seahawks, the Cowboys' hot streak and Peyton Manning's record-breaking night.
